entry.stringvalue: audio/x-raw-int,rate=44100,channels=2 ! twolame name=enc mode=0 bitrate=192 ! id3v2mux

entry.name: description
entry.stringvalue: Used for converting to CD-quality audio, but with the lossy MP2 codec. Use this for preparing files for copying to devices that only support the MP2 codec. Note that using this format may be illegal in your jurisdiction; contact your lawyer for advice.
